  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Office Hysteroscopy is associated with a level of anxiety that could condition tolerability
      of the procedure by the patient.

      The aim of this study is to evaluate the impact of music on anxiety state, expected and
      received pain by patients during office hysteroscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
